    {
        "id":"tunlon_start_1",
        "message":"Hello kid! How are you?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Fine, thank you. Who are you?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_start_2",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"tunlon_fence",
                        "value":10,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"Good. Do you have anything to trade?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_trade"
            },
            {
                "text":"Have you seen Andor, my brother? He looks a bit ...",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_andor",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"tunlon_fence",
                        "value":20,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_start_2",
        "message":"I am Tunlon of Crossglen. I look after my flock of sheep here.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I am from Crossglen too!",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_1",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"tunlon_fence",
                        "value":10,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"Nice to have met you.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"tunlon_fence",
                        "value":10
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_andor",
        "message":"I know Andor. Of course I do.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_andor_2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_andor_2",
        "message":"Always good for mischief, that boy.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Yes, that's him. Do you know where he is?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_andor_3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_andor_3",
        "message":"No. And I want to keep it that way.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Oh. What has he done to you?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_andor_4"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_andor_4",
        "message":"He scared my sheep. They didn't dare to leave the stable for two weeks.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_andor_5"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_andor_5",
        "message":"I then confronted him, even though I was a little scared myself.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"And then?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_andor_6"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_andor_6",
        "message":"And then? Nothing. With a look that made my blood run cold, he left.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Yes, my beloved brother. Who are you by the way?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_start_2",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"tunlon_fence",
                        "value":10,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"Then that's settled. Another question: Do you have anything to trade?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_trade"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_trade",
        "message":"Yes, I have a few basic supplies that I could offer. Do you want to have a look?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Sure!",
                "nextPhraseID":"S"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_1",
        "message":"That is great to hear. Could you by any chance get me something from Crossglen? Unfortunately I have to stay here to watch my sheep.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Oh yeah, no problem!",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_2"
            },
            {
                "text":"Sorry, I have other things to do right now.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_noquest"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_2",
        "message":"Thank you, kid. What I need is some wood to repair my fence.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Where do I get that from?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_3",
        "message":"Oh, isn't there a lumberjack in Crossglen anymore? I haven't been down there for a long time",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Maybe this explains why the forest around Crossglen is too dense to get through...",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_3a"
            },
            {
                "text":"At least not that I know.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_4"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_3a",
        "message":"What do you mean? The climb into the mountains is just northeast of Crossglen?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Maybe it used to be like that.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_3b"
            },
            {
                "text":"If there was a path, it has long since become overgrown.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_3b"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_3b",
        "message":"What do you mean?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I had to take a long detour past Stoutford and Prim and come from the other side.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_3c"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_3c",
        "message":"Then it's a good thing that I haven't tried to go down to Crossglen with my sheep in recent years.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"In any case, there is no lumberjack in Crossglen.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_4"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_4",
        "message":"Well, then you would have to travel over to Fallhaven. Of course only, if that's not too much for you.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Not for me! I know the way perfectly well.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_5"
            },
            {
                "text":"Hmm, now that I think about it ...",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_4a"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_4a",
        "message":"Please don't let me down. There are wolves and worse here threatening my sheep.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Sigh, I have too good a heart. It's okay, I'll do it.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_5"
            },
            {
                "text":"No, forget it. I'm out.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_quest_4b"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_4b",
        "message":"A pity. Come back if you change your mind."
    },
    {
        "id":"tunlon_quest_5",
        "message":"Thank you so much! Here is a bit of gold so you can pay for it.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I will go and get it now.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            },
            {
                "text":"Hehe, thank you!",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
