                "text":"Here, I hope these are better.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tunlon_prog_22",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"inventoryRemove",
                        "requireID":"tunlon_fence2",
                        "value":10
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"No, I am still looking for them.",
